Description.p:
SIF_ConditionGroup represents the conditions that the queried object(s) must meet.
If conditions are specified, only those objects that meet the conditions are returned;
otherwise, all objects of the specified name are returned.

tr.td:
If SIF_Query/SIF_ConditionGroup exists, place it in SIF_ExtendedQuery/SIF_Where setting
@ObjectName
to SIF_Query/SIF_QueryObject/@ObjectName in every occurrence of SIF_Element.
